{%- comment -%}
  Ganguram — Shipping ESTIMATE config (Phase 2.11I).

  Publishes window.GanguramEstimateConfig (the LOCAL Standard-delivery slabs + the 4-hour
  radius / flat price + cache settings) and loads assets/ganguram-shipping-estimate.js — the
  pure, config-driven mapping used by the delivery-popup estimate and the pincode-area
  distance range. Change the slabs / 4-hour radius HERE; no JS edit needed.

  ESTIMATE / display only — ShipZip remains the source of the FINAL checkout rate. No
  checkout / ShipZip / service-code (4HR/STD) / MOV / pincode-eligibility / product-
  visibility / date-picker-attribute change. Fail-open (no Google / API failure ->
  "Final charge confirmed at checkout").
{%- endcomment -%}
<script>
  window.GanguramEstimateConfig = {
    // LOCAL Standard-delivery slabs — cumulative km upper bounds, whole rupees.
    // 0–5 km ₹50 · 5.01–10 km ₹70 · 10.01–15 km ₹100 · 15.01–20 km ₹150.
    standardSlabs: [
      { maxKm: 5,  price: 50 },
      { maxKm: 10, price: 70 },
      { maxKm: 15, price: 100 },
      { maxKm: 20, price: 150 }
    ],
    // 4-hour (quick-commerce) — admin-configurable. enabled toggles it; maxDistanceKm is the
    // serviceable driving radius (change to e.g. 20 to allow 4-hour up to 20 km); flatPrice ₹.
    // A full address within maxDistanceKm shows 4 Hours only when ALL cart items are Quick
    // Commerce. ShipZip + time-window rules still gate the actual checkout offer.
    fourHour: { enabled: true, maxDistanceKm: 10, flatPrice: 10 },
    // PAN India weight estimate: pricePerUnit per perWeightG grams (₹80 per 500 g).
    panIndia: { perWeightG: 500, pricePerUnit: 80 },
    // Slab-safety margin (km): a full-address driving distance is biased UP by this much BEFORE
    // matching a Standard slab, so a ~15 km address the Routes API returns as 14.9 km is never
    // under-quoted at the 10–15 km (₹100) tier instead of the 15–20 km (₹150) tier. DISPLAY
    // ESTIMATE only — ShipZip remains the final checkout rate, so the bias only errs toward NOT
    // under-quoting. Set to 0 for the exact route distance. Applies to a single full address,
    // not the pincode-area range (the range already brackets uncertainty with its max end).
    slabSafetyMarginKm: 0.3,
    currencySymbol: "₹",
    rangeSeparator: "–",      // en dash
    cacheVersion: 1,               // bump to invalidate cached pincode-area estimates
    cacheTtlMs: 86400000,          // 24h — don't re-call Google for the same pincode
    sampleEdgeMidpoints: false     // sample centre + 4 corners (5 points); true -> + 4 edge midpoints
  };
</script>
<script src="{{ 'ganguram-shipping-estimate.js' | asset_url }}" defer></script>
